description:
## Objective
Build comprehensive tag dictionary from CRYSTAL23 manual.

## Categories

### Structure Keywords
CRYSTAL, SLAB, POLYMER, MOLECULE, HELIX, EXTERNAL, SUPERCEL, NANOTUBE

### Geometry Keywords  
OPTGEOM, FULLOPTG, CELLONLY, ATOMONLY, CVOLOPT, INTRANS, ELASTIC

### Hamiltonian Keywords
DFT, EXCHANGE, CORRELAT, SPIN, LSDA
- Functionals: B3LYP, PBE, PBESOL, HSE06, M06, PW91, LDA
- Hybrid: HFEXCHANGE, AEXX

### SCF Keywords
TOLINTEG, TOLPSEUD, FMIXING, BROYDEN, DIIS, ANDERSON
SHRINK, MAXCYCLE, LEVSHIFT, SPINLOCK

### Basis Set Keywords
BASISSET, SHELL, GHOSTS, ECP

### Properties Keywords
BAND, DOSS, POTC, ECHG, COOP, BWDF, ANISOTRO

## Data Structure
\`\`\`typescript
interface CrystalTag {
  name: string;
  category: 'structure' | 'geometry' | 'hamiltonian' | 'scf' | 'basis' | 'properties';
  type: 'keyword' | 'block' | 'value';
  valueType?: 'int' | 'float' | 'bool' | 'string' | 'array';
  description: string;
  defaultValue?: any;
  validValues?: any[];
  deprecated?: boolean;
  seeAlso?: string[];
}
\`\`\`

## Source
- CRYSTAL23 User Manual
- crystal23.unito.it documentation
